##CPGE_SCRIPT
##ScriptVersion: 1.0
##Written: 2026-05-10
##Scene: SCENE_INTRO
##Author: LordAries1972
##Description: Intro cinematic — camera choreography, full-screen FX sequence, LABEL/GOTO demo.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Camera starting position for intro flythrough
# POSITION x y z yaw pitch
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
POSITION 0.0 10.0 -30.0 0.0 -15.0

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Hold black for half a second, then fade in
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Execute FadeToBlack(0.0, 0.0)
Execute FadeToImage(3.0, 0.5)

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Warp dot tunnel during the intro
# InitWarpDotTunnel(x, y, z, minRadius, maxRadius, spinCycle, travelSpeed,
#                   reverseTravel, dotsPerCircle, density)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
LABEL TunnelStart:
Execute InitWarpDotTunnel(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 5.0, 80.0, Clockwise, 3, false, 24, 3)

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Animated camera sweep — rotate 45 degrees on Y over speed 2
# RotateY(degrees, speed, focusOnTarget)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Execute RotateY(45.0, 2, false)
WAIT(4.0)
Execute StopWarpDotTunnel()
Execute StopRotating()

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Audio
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Execute StartPlaybackThread()
Execute SetGlobalVolume(0.9)

ALERT General "Intro sequence running."

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# LABEL / GOTO example:
# In a real script a condition check would decide whether to loop.
# GOTO TunnelStart would restart the tunnel sequence from the top.
# Shown here commented out to avoid an actual infinite loop in the demo.
# Uncomment and pair with a conditional mechanism when the IF command
# is introduced in a future ScriptManager version.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# GOTO TunnelStart
